Legend:
  W = Work in progress
  D = Done
  P = Postponed
  ? = Questionable

Plans for 0.5.0
===============

  * Test all stuff
  * Print set_sensitivities
  * Profile
  * PyLint, py.test
  * Put a .pot file in the trunk?
  * Mime-type registration?
  * Non-lib stuff
  * setup.py:
      - Don't install any testing
      - python 2.5 uninstall?
      - Remove setup.cfg?
      - Destination vs. configure (e.g. Arch)
          - setup.py install --prefix=/usr --root=tmp/pkg
      - Use intltool-merge for gaupol.desktop file translations
          - See alacarte source code
      - clean command
      - Do setup.py install options work?

  New:
    [W] Find and replace
    [D] Encoding autodetection: http://chardet.feedparser.org/

  Changes:
    [D] New icon
    [D] Applied GNOME Goal 2.1: Install theme-friendly icons
    [D] Support default browsers on KDE and Mac OSX as well
    [D] Better video player defaults on Windows
    [W] Framerate conversion available for time-based subs as well
    [D] Developer-specific options to gaupol made into separate scripts
    [W] Testing framework made compatible with py.test
    [D] Desktop file strings are now extracted to .po files
    [D] Time decimal changed from "," to "."
    [D] Video selection dialog's file filter should default to video
    [D] Gaupol hangs if video player not closed before exit
    [D] Spell-check suggestion list does not scroll to top with new word
    [D] Icon field in the desktop file should not include extension
    [D] Debug dialog fails to start if PyEnchant not installed
    [D] Dialog sizes smallerable
    [D] Remove Unselect All menu item?
    [D] Sort on open feedback
    [D] Save a copy removed
    [D] Spell-check dialog mnemonics: Join _Back, Join _Forward
    [D] Dialog targets
    [D] Fixed menu ellipses
    [D] General polish here and there
    [D] Separate header template files
    [D] Fixed spell-check recursion bugs

  Dependencies:
    [W] Psyco no longer used
    [D] Universal Encoding Detector >= 1.0

  New Translations:
    [D] Polish (po)


